These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, romance
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, april
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Movie-Genre       | romance       | zombie |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Birthday       | april    | january    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
2 different games are played: go, chess
2 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person playing go is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Game           | go | chess      |
| Pet   | mouse  | hamster      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, entrepreneur
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the entrepreneur##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Flower   | poppy  | dahlia   |
| Job     | entrepreneur     | teacher |

