.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, nigerian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, badminton
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the polish##1
3. the nigerian is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Nationality      | polish       | nigerian |
| Sport          | badminton         | sailing    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

