.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-19::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, chess
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball
2 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Hobby           | reading  | chess   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | salsa      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| Game     | mah-jongg     | backgammon |

